<abstract>
<para>
&kapplication; is an akonadi agent which allows to store individual emails in an archive folder.
</para>
</abstract>

<keywordset>
<keyword>KDE</keyword>
<keyword>KMail</keyword>
<keyword>Archive</keyword>
</keywordset>

